      • getAutoTieringPolicyName

        public java.lang.String getAutoTieringPolicyName()
        The auto tier policy name. Only supported for VMAX and VNX storage systems. If auto_tiering_policy_name is specified, then on VNX, a ranking algorithm is applied to get matching pools. On VMAX, only pools associated with VMAX Auto Tier Policies are matched.

      • getMultiVolumeConsistency

        public java.lang.Boolean getMultiVolumeConsistency()
        Specifies whether or not the virtual pool supports multi-volume consistency. When specified for a virtual pool, volumes created using the virtual pool can be created in consistency groups.
